{% comment %}
  Schema settings for the product-card-add-to-cart snippet.
  Copy the settings below into your theme's main-collection (or featured-collection)
  section, inside the "settings" array in the section's {% schema %}.

  Setting IDs used by the snippet (with defaults if missing):
  - card_radius (number, default 12)
  - card_padding (number, default 16)
  - card_border (checkbox, default true)
  - card_bg (color, default #ffffff)
  - card_border_color (color, default #e5e5e5)
  - card_shadow (select: none, subtle, medium, strong)
  - card_gap (number, default 10)
  - card_info_gap (number, default 8)
  - product_card_button_bg (color, optional – uses theme button/scheme if blank)
  - product_card_button_text_color (color, optional)
  - product_card_button_radius (number, default 8)
  - product_card_button_size (select: small, medium, large)
  - product_card_button_full_width (checkbox, default true)
{% endcomment %}
